thread.title: David Berube
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by David Berube

author: David Berube
title: David Berube
text: I've been a customer of Mystery Tackle Box for about 8 months now. Every month around the 13th or 14th I can expect to receive my shipment of fishing lures from them. The value of the lures far exceeds how much I'm paying for them and, being new to fishing, I haven't even used some of the types of equipment they send. So it's always a delight to make my way out to the water to try out some new stuff. I'd highly recommend them to any dedicated or hobbyist fisherman.
